* Add gameplay deadlock detection code.

* Finish the keyboard interface within the GUI.

* Create the simulator.

* Improve the build system.

* Add prefix-independence code for Unix-like systems.

* Improve the graphical user interface.

* Create an icon for Morris Sim.

* Improve user-level documentation.

* Add a half-duplex terminal interface and socket support for network
  play.

* Finish the Spanish translations.

* Add Python bindings.

* Add a Scheme/GUILE interface.  For MIT Scheme, this can only be done
  through sockets and a Scheme interface file for the socket
  connection.

